lead_paragraph: Dustin Johnson's "ridiculous" ability to overpower golf courses with his length and precision could be the key to American Ryder Cup glory this week, according to twice U.S. Open winner Andy North.

headline.print_headline: Golf: Johnson's Form Could Be U.S. Trump Card-North
